<!--
  Harvest Tool Example Policy File

  This policy file corresponds with the test bundles generated by the 
  Atmospheres Node. By specifying the bundle products below, Harvest 
  relies on the bundles correctly specifying the collections and the 
  collections correctly specifying the products.

  $Id$
-->

<policy>
